The soft buttery striped knit has random silver stars and bursts out with a cotton pink tutu, embellished with an organza flower.  If you want to wear it as a sundress, I'd go a size up.  If you want it as a tunic/top its pretty true to size.  This pairs adorable with leggings and ballet flats.  I also sell the leggings! check out my other items.

name: Misha Lulu Plus Pin by M.O.M. Handmade
description:
each pin is individually screen printed on cotton muslin and the rosey cheeks are painted by hand; backed with colorful remnant or vintage fabric; stuffed with poly fill; pin back closure.

this is our favorite product from the collaboration we did with the l.a. based clothing company misha lulu for their spring 2013 line.

we adore everything misha lulu and we were stoked to say the least when karen and joe (the owners and designers) said yes to collaborating with m.o.m!

made in encinitas, california

name: Woodland Cookie Cutter Set
description:
Who doesn't love a good woodland theme? This set of 6 cookie cutters is great for holiday baking or to give as a gift. Each set comes packaged in a pink bakery box with brown baker's twine. Hand wash and dry.

Our woodland set includes a gnome (5"), an owl (3 1/4"), a squirrel (3 3/4"), a deer (4"), a mushroom (3 1/2") and a pine tree (3 1/2").

name: Cloth Baby Doll - Dorothy The Unicorn Hunter
description:
Dorothy was handmade with 100% cotton canvas and stuffed with polyfil. Her hair is made of acrylic yarn and her dress was made using vintage fabric and trims.

Dorothy comes with a little bunny pocket friend to keep her occupied when you are busy.

She measures 22 inches (45 cm)

name: Retractable Tape Measure Maple Tree
description:
This is the cutest tape measure you could ever own. I keep mine in my purse! You NEVER know when you might need it.

Pull the trunk and the tape measure extends to 60", then press the hidden button on the back and it retracks back into the leafy green part of the tree.

Dimensions of the tree tape measure are, 4 1/2" by 3"

name: Tree Stump Felt Coasters
description:
Each stump slice features a lovely spiral pattern with a heart in the center machine top stitched.  The edges have been lovingly hand stitched to give the outer edge the look of tree bark.

These coasters can withstand high temperatures,  you can also use them as small hot pads.

All four coasters come in a cute little bundle. These are made of  100% wool felt in "brown sugar". Perfect for gift giving. The coasters measure about 4 inches (10.16 cm) in diameter.

name: Pink and White Taxidermy Unicorn Head
description:
This unicorn was hand stitched using 35% wool 65% rayon. Acrylic yarn is twisted and tied as hair, and held with handmade bows. Flat round black button eyes, peek out of pink eyelids. This unicorn head rests on a hand painted plaque, ready to be hung!


Measures 5" by 3" (12.7 cm X 7.62cm)

name: Brown and Yellow Taxidermy Unicorn Head
description:
This unicorn was hand stitched using 35% wool 65% rayon.  Acrylic yarn  is twisted and tied as hair, and held with handmade bows. Flat round black button eyes, peek out of wool brown eye lids.  This unicorn head rests on a hand painted heart plaque, ready to be hung! 

Measures 5" by 5" (12.7 cm X 12.7 cm

name: Pink and Purple Taxidermy Unicorn Head
description:
This little unicorn was lovingly hand made in the U.S.A 
 
Hand stitched using 35% wool 65% rayon felt with acrylic yarn hair and button eyes.

Measures 4" by 4" (10.6 cm X 10.6 cm

name: Tree Stump Pincushion
description:
This is a sweet little tree stump pincushion! 

The body is made with 100% wool.  The wood grain is machine stitched as well as the top stitching of the tree circles and heart. Top and bottom are made of felt that has been up cycled from recycled plastic bottles! 
Mr. tree stump is filled with Fairfield Poly-Pellets on the bottom to give weight so he doesn't move when removing pins. The rest is filled with Fairfield Poly-fil allowing pins to slide in and out with ease.

Mr. stump also features a sweet little branch with one little moss green leaf made of 70% wool felt. 

Measurements are as follows:
3.5 inches (8.89 centimeters) tall and 2.5 inches (6.35 centimeters) in diameter at the base. Tree stump gets slightly narrower at the top.

Each pincushion comes with one sweet little mushroom pin. Colors may vary due to availability.

hitree items are made with lots of love and well intentions.

name: Wool Log Bolster Pillow
description:
Wool Log Bolster Roll Pillow

This log pillow was handmade in the U.S.A. using 100% wool. The wood grain was machine stitched as well as the little brown hearts all along the grain. Super cute! The ends were stitched by hand adding a bark texture to the seams.

This is the PERFECT pillow for an epic pillow fight or to accent a woodland themed room or nursery.

The log is 16.5 inches (41.91 cm) long and approximately 5 inches (12.7 cm) wide.
Stuffed with hypoallergenic poly-fil.

name: Mr. Giant Sequoia
description:
Giant Sequoias are known to be one of the largest and oldest living organisms on earth. With the largest documented tree reaching 311 feet tall and about 3,000 years old.

Mr. Giant Sequoia is made from the highest quality wool felt from my own original design. He is stuffed with hypoallergenic polyester fiberfill.

Mr. Giant Sequoia measures 19 inches tall (48.26cm) by 13 inches wide (33.02cm)

name: Pine Tree Plush Toy by hitree
description:
This is Mr. Pine Tree. He is very friendly, almost to a fault.

He enjoys making up songs about pine cones to sing to his forest friends while trying to grow taller.

Mr. Pine Tree is 15 inches (38.1 cm) tall an 12 inches (30.5 cm) wide and made from high quality wool felt. He is stuffed with hypoallergenic polyester fiberfill.

name: Maple Tree Friend Plush Toy
description:
Mr. Maple Tree Friend Plush Toy would love to be your friend.

He enjoys cuddling and making up songs about unicorns. He is the perfect addition to your woodland themed children's room or nursery.

Mr. Maple Tree was handmade using high quality wool felt and stuffed with hypoallergenic poly-fil.

9" tall by 7" wide.
